<body>
    <h1>Task 19 - RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"c0476a3d1e41" id=3D"Task19-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"d2ede125a231" id=3D"Task19-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3057f73588e7">The purpose of this document is to define the =
requirements for setting up a <strong>Grafana alerting system integrated wi=
th multiple email delivery mechanisms</strong>, including a <strong>self-ho=
sted SMTP mail server, AWS SES, and AWS WorkMail with SNS</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"69d38a190e22">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bf0a8da3276c">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0ed4082d5d4b">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f59977291955">Monitoring/Observability Teams</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"85626c933d86">Students and Interns</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"36d211d9eba5" id=3D"Task19-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"106e1d9c4ee6"><strong>Included in scope:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"eb18832795ae">Self-hosted mail server setup (SMTP)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"27a2b3e496a4">Grafana SMTP configuration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4b631a34fbce">AWS SES email setup</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"18d5f5352e99">AWS WorkMail + SNS integration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"654fb3e216ad">Alert testing and validation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a48a6b06e847"><strong>Not included:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"99781ecb0c84">Advanced email security (DKIM, SPF deep config=
)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7b3be6b1b51e">High availability mail server setup</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d6a66c17294e">Complex alert rules or dashboards</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"f666b477b74c" id=3D"Task19-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"d=
476acd8-6c16-4521-bb4b-5a89564cc5e6" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"396fc4f42b2d">Term</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"eccae391928a">Meaning</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ef270b82c83a">SMTP</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"34226c130ac5">Simple Mail Transfer Protocol</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f670a6333a0e">SES</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c434d036e05a">Simple Email Service</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"30e1298e8a50">SNS</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b1ba96469d68">Simple Notification Service</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"67dc1ca95c33">Grafana</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"222181df5fdf">Monitoring and alerting tool</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3b627b245107">WorkMail</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cff88866dd77">AWS enterprise email service</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"a9ee5109f3e0" id=3D"Task19-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f85cf8dae550">Grafana Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b084b58750a2">AWS SES Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"95d7ce8b576d">AWS SNS Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"61ccb3f22f52">AWS WorkMail Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7a54942d0c79">Postfix Documentation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"bfff0d9b70db" id=3D"Task19-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"beda8f51732b">This document describes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7aded99c32d6">Alerting architecture</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5e73f21863da">Email delivery mechanisms</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"546c034efa28">Functional and non-functional requirements</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"84ee244e5eb2">Validation and testing</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"ed902573d0ca" id=3D"Task19-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"966e5ae26b8f" id=3D"Task19-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5b12989301c6">Set up a self-hosted SMTP mail server</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5411c6cd54ff">Configure Grafana to send alerts via SMTP</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"765c74661f1c">Configure AWS SES for email delivery</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d4366c8fb962">Configure AWS WorkMail with SNS</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"46a967087299">Validate alert delivery across all systems</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"2f47b79198ce" id=3D"Task19-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"98812f2212ef">Ensure reliable alert delivery</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"abc88669c247">Compare different email solutions</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"528b41b580b1">Improve monitoring system efficiency</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e508b766396c">Enable scalable and flexible alerting</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"66d98a5e0425" id=3D"Task19-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8f45b33dc4a0">ABC Technologies uses Grafana for monitoring b=
ut needs to evaluate different email delivery systems.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6dc7aa20a231">Currently, alerts may not be reliable or scala=
ble.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3ef0a40a7fe7">This project explores:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fd91c232fca4">Self-hosted email control</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"900adadc7a8c">Cloud-based scalable email (SES)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d283682e9f61">Enterprise email solution (WorkMail)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"325542ef3a87" id=3D"Task19-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9d4a555c311b">AWS service limits (SES sandbox mode)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"eaab5a907f88">Email delivery delays</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b60d7d2bb9b2">SMTP configuration complexity</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b8f1ff92606e">Domain verification requirements</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"e6c5a73b83fb" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"4e7cf9123bd9" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h2><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-cente=
r-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedde=
d-image image-center" alt=3D"undefined-20260321-125249.png" width=3D"468" l=
oading=3D"lazy" src=3D"0b1bacb214994b41bd56354875cad5d9b43ce5bdc5f496ef5c12=
715b406a261b" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/=
attachments/1879539766/undefined-20260321-125249.png?version=3D1&amp;modifi=
cationDate=3D1774097988154&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=
