eight=3D"248"></span>
<p local-id=3D"490dbb589ecb"></p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"98f0950dd66b" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.2UseCases">3.2 Use Cases</=
h2>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"f1040aa4c39b" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.2.1UseCase1:SetupSMTPServe=
r">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Setup SMTP Server</h3>
<p local-id=3D"43e7a94a9803"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Configure a self-hosted mail server for sending emails.</p>
<p local-id=3D"330e57f43c3e"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"baa05a67ef9d">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7924a836e858"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e0109ad1ab2a">EC2 instance available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"579581559fcf"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1389086d57c2">SMTP server can send emails</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ea93eea9c821"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8caa22cbd557">Launch EC2 instance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d6380b9e0a3e">Install Postfix</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"41a356bd77b5">Configure SMTP settings</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0ee540314037">Enable authentication</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fa13b5b8deb5">Test email sending</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"16202ef35b4c"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1265da78d03c">Mail delivery failure</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"7c1572402ba9" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.2.2UseCase2:ConfigureGrafa=
naSMTP">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Configure Grafana SMTP</h3>
<p local-id=3D"2fc75e5b6e5a"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Integrate Grafana with SMTP server.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7392c17e4379"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bdcc44c9cda7">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"48621a99dd37"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a74cf14db6f8">SMTP server running</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"eb9ae4d3e478"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b225baef71a9">Grafana sends alerts via SMTP</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4cd9d9f89270"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2d1cf7937a89">Update Grafana config file</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8ddcc6b290e8">Add SMTP credentials</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"44d299a3ab35">Restart Grafana</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"48030f6c2792">Create test alert</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"28beb4f6bca2">Verify email</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"dd80ed637245"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"156e2eff12f6">Incorrect credentials</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"4c0df26880bb" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.2.3UseCase3:SetupAWSSES">3=
.2.3 Use Case 3: Setup AWS SES</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b4c9b46404d1"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Configure AWS SES for email delivery.</p>
<p local-id=3D"86cf96a7dca3"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0fbc49f2f064">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d9a080b81203"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5700c5701efe">AWS account available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"434dd2b159a4"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a08db11c9e35">SES can send emails</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d8cdd3c789f5"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"98a68d9e86f5">Verify email/domain</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e3df60a5e019">Enable sending permissions</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8f0810dd49c2">Create SNS topic</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"26620af8c2b6">Subscribe email</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0755f2d85e99">Test email delivery</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"7e64984a1dfb"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6e6dd9a59b66">SES sandbox restriction</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"0345c7903fa1" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.2.4UseCase4:SetupAWSWorkMa=
il+SNS">3.2.4 Use Case 4: Setup AWS WorkMail + SNS</h3>
<p local-id=3D"48ed68746e1d"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Configure WorkMail for enterprise email.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ad1749814671"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"11a446471710">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1967409943f0"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b079d98bae35">AWS account available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"52fadda5d18d"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6160273df14b">WorkMail receives alerts</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9c5b341929bc"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bd5a02358064">Create WorkMail organization</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c833d650c9b4">Create mailbox</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bd44aac3679b">Configure SNS topic</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d5c2afb71b9a">Subscribe WorkMail email</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d779ac64c7db">Test email</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"b2c7b35c8d5d"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9d3370a0d1a8">Mailbox configuration error</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"cd969b5d29d9" id=3D"Task19-RAD-3.2.5UseCase5:TriggerGrafana=
Alerts">3.2.5 Use Case 5: Trigger Grafana Alerts</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c99ae0042ccd"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Generate alerts from Grafana.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f96366178393"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"30366a04ef87">Grafana</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b6b697f710c6">User</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"50ea6d4bf19b"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7ef2e91ce797">Alert rules configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"016c537869ba"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f2f6eb96b0ba">Alerts triggered</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"23f7cb0d5697"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6713b6707aec">Define alert rule</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c671f8e1dd20">Set threshold (CPU, errors)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"88fcff0fe00a">Trigger alert</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2dbbf81eb7c0">Send notification</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"229c570a42f7"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"845a046e3be3">Alert not triggered</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"262470643277" id=3D"Task19-RAD-4.Non-FunctionalRequirements=
">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"84a1978b81bf" id=3D"Task19-RAD-4.1PerformanceRequirements">=
4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e663f3a6ed67">Fast alert delivery</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b06563ac8164">Minimal delay in email notifications</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ec6504fd60b0">Efficient processing</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"582d0d275ed4" id=3D"Task19-RAD-4.2SecurityRequirements">4.2=
 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d3ed05a61003">Secure SMTP authentication</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"21aa15cd1b32">AWS IAM permissions</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c2d6f0ef2ed1">Protected email credentials</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"32896bf472e6" id=3D"Task19-RAD-4.3UsabilityRequirements">4.=
3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"67dc65720e73">Easy Grafana configuration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"171d72e23b95">Simple alert creation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c63992eb5353">Clear email notifications</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"d17691985e31" id=3D"Task19-RAD-4.4ReliabilityRequirements">=
4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e4ed6b038292">High email delivery success rate</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5b7daa7250cb">Multiple providers for redundancy</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"68bd0b5b6309">Consistent alert system</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"c182bcc87369" id=3D"Task19-RAD-4.5ComplianceRequirements">4=
.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"96cd45d54edf">Follow email sending policies</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d6766eff23f1">Avoid spam issues</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"84ef6162db12">Proper domain verification</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"79d9ccbd4b74" id=3D"Task19-RAD-5.AssumptionsandDependencies=
">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"87f997ea94a3" id=3D"Task19-RAD-5.1Assumptions">5.1 Assumpti=
ons</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"aef2152d921e">AWS services available</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"937c9bf7d4a6">Internet connectivity</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e3716eeb6da6">Grafana installed</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"7dd705fba731" id=3D"Task19-RAD-5.2Dependencies">5.2 Depende=
ncies</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4bf2fae6bf47">AWS SES</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"33638637bbf4">AWS SNS</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"97fbe41d212e">AWS WorkMail</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fff1f3de5192">SMTP server (Postfix)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a69b2f1788da">Grafana</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"51a6659eac96" id=3D"Task19-RAD-6.RiskAnalysis">6. Risk Anal=
ysis</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"4f64c6d373c9" id=3D"Task19-RAD-6.1RiskIdentification">6.1 R=
isk Identification</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f85d5b2f09fd">Email delivery failure</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"33ac8fa17dbb">SES sandbox limitations</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"abef125d5810">SMTP misconfiguration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d148f3f18310">SNS subscription issues</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"45061845c758" id=3D"Task19-RAD-6.2RiskMitigation">6.2 Risk =
Mitigation</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ede9fde3f8fc">Test each system independently</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"aea340e1c734">Move SES out of sandbox</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"925afdef0ebe">Validate configurations</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"83bfd2ca2444">Monitor logs</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
